[b]Players home.

[/b]Entrance to AFLAND "Portal Gem Door" is located at Helgen,see picture for more info.

[b]Installation: [/b]Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,then you have to extract it into your data                       file for Skyrim.

U[b]nistallation:[/b]  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.

My Regards to you all.

Thank You.
